  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is assess the severity of osteoarthritic knee between one-leg and
      both-leg standing radiograph in primary OA knee
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      All patients were performed digital radiographs which one-leg and both-leg standing
      anteroposterior view. Medial and lateral joint space width were measured. The severity of OA
      knee was identified by the Kellgren-Lawrence (KL) classification.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
